## Start a game

modes:

- play against AI
- play against another player
- play between two AIs +nbr of times



spawn PlayerA
spawn PlayerB

player = pickFirstPlayer()

while game not finished or max turn not reached
    coordinates = ask player coordinates (send "your turn\n")
    validateCoordinates(coordinates) -> if invalid player looses

    response = get (other) player response
    validateResponse("miss/hit/sunk/won/error")

    acknowledgement = send back response
    validateAcknoledgement("ok/error")

